name: DEEPCOOL MATREXX 55 Gaming Case
desc: Matrexx 55 Mesh ADD-RGB 4F is a high airflow case that comes with an included A-RGB lighting system and full size tempered glass.

name: A320M-HDV R4.0  Motherboard
desc: The PCIe Gen3 x4 Ultra M.2 interface pushes data transfer speeds up to 32Gb/s. In addition, it also supports SATA3 6Gb/s M.2 modules, and is compatible with ASRock’s U.2 Kit for installing some of the world’s fastest U.2 PCIe Gen3 x4 SSDs

name: i3-12100 12th Gen Alder Lake Processor
desc: The latest Core i3-12100 12th Gen Alder Lake Processor features 4 cores and 8 threads. The CPU will operate at a base frequency of 3.30 GHz and a maximum boost frequency of up to 4.30 GHz

name: Z1 ARGB 120mm Casing Fan
desc: The  Z1 ARGB Casing Fan features a Dual-Ring Design. The dual ring lighting effect design makes the outstanding visual performance. It delivers 1200 RPM ± 10% speed and has a noise level of 25 dBA which makes it functional and quiet

name: SPARK AIO Lite ARGB 240mn CPU Liquid Cooler
desc: The ZADAK SPARK AIO Lite ARGB 240mn CPU Liquid Cooler offers an alternative cooling solution for end users all over the world who are suffering from overheating issues.

name: 1TB 3.5 Surveillance Hard Drive
desc: Seagate SkyHawk 1TB Surveillance Hard Drive - SATA 6Gb/s 64MB Cache 3.5-Inch Internal Drive Custom-built for surveillance applications with Image Perfect firmware for crisp, clear, 24×7 video workloads

name: FURY Beast 16GB 5200MHz DDR5 Desktop RAM
desc: FURY Beast comes with 16GB Capacity, 5200MHz Speed, DDR5 Type, and CL40 Latency. The Desktop RAM supports Intel Extreme Memory Profiles (Intel XMP) 3.0. and also this RAM has been tested to run at DDR5-5200 at low latency

name: GeForce RTX 3070 Ti MASTER 8GB GDDR6X Graphics Card
desc: AORUS GeForce RTX 3070 Ti MASTER features MAX-Covered cooling. The MAX-Covered cooling features two 115mm and one 100mm unique blade stack fans with wind claw design and alternate spinning, so the air pressure can completely cover the heatsink
